RUN /bin/sh -c set -eux; 		savedAptMark="$(apt-mark showmanual)"; 	apt-get update; 	apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends 		bzip2 		dpkg-dev 		gcc 		gnupg 		libapr1-dev 		libaprutil1-dev 		libbrotli-dev 		libcurl4-openssl-dev 		libjansson-dev 		liblua5.2-dev 		libnghttp2-dev 		libpcre3-dev 		libssl-dev 		libxml2-dev 		make 		patch 		wget 		zlib1g-dev 	;
